{"tid":318232,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《搏盡無悔？笑話》","createTime":"2017-07-12T03:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T03:37:52.000Z","uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b76a0ad1f589f716d1876779444f39f0ff4a8412","tid":318232,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"好多人話搏盡無悔，但係事實呢？<br />\n我叫耀揚，唔係蠱惑仔，只係咁啱撞名。今年考完dse。<br />\n記得中四我經常上facebook，嗰啲咩網絡傳媒喺dse期間成撚日話咩搏盡無悔，但有好多戇鳩仔係度又like又comment，我心諗：屌你咩，完全係誤人子弟，意思係搏盡就唔洗理成績？搏盡無悔？留低同你將來老細講啦，睇下佢請唔請你？啲人洗唔洗咁鍾意打飛機啊？<br />\n從此就唔太上fb。<br />\n之後識左幾嗰大學生。<br />\n《未完待續》"},{"pid":"407812bb048a1552f7acef9f558bf4bb45c89126","tid":318232,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次出故，歡迎俾意見，不喜勿插<br />\nbtw：本故事純屬虛構，如有雷同實屬不辛"},{"pid":"03aee8226b3008f610ffd697e6fb107a22d35ae3","tid":318232,"uid":12979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"得個一細段學人出故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1951caf93d4590276b9340f41ee82fa87ae82d","tid":318232,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"話說識左班大學生，佢哋同我講U Life有幾好剩，又話佢哋一開始都好似我咁，唔撚柒讀書，係最尾一、兩年先俾心機讀書，有嗰仲誇張，話數學最尾3個月爆，但攞左5，我都知好大水份，但都燃起我既讀書之路。<br />\n其中一個女仔叫Emily，老實講，我一開始唔太想識佢，但機緣巧合下我同佢傾過兩句，慢慢冇咁抗拒佢，佢理科底，咁啱我數學當時最差，跟著我就同幾個有心讀書既同學一齊搵佢補數，諗著搏3or4。<br />\n《未完待續》"},{"pid":"38c82163e6a8d8099ce96d0d813d905d5dc9e06b","tid":318232,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得個一細段學人出故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係街度，出得慢，sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e2b80078701badbfa22586084ea0a7ad2bd626","tid":318232,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"今晚翻屋企打多兩段"},{"pid":"15db8ff8d19d5d474a519c580a45dd78b95178b0","tid":318232,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"why負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}